  "focus_spans": [
    {
      "end_byte": 1537,
      "focus_id": "F001",
      "source_text": "这样处理的好处是，",
      "source_text_sha256": "7d4eba9700dd25f191d99989cd40a25b0e0900d561d2a00239b8c1f3cad5347b",
      "start_byte": 1510
    },
    {
      "end_byte": 3198,
      "focus_id": "F002",
      "source_text": "同时，参数扫描的写法也要服务于结论表达。",
      "source_text_sha256": "34c20e2348aafba3362cf8959cf10c74f0c7e4505196cb63f082de9b5b38df72",
      "start_byte": 3138
    },
    {
      "end_byte": 4070,
      "focus_id": "F003",
      "source_text": "这样处理后，问题四的表述就会自然从“某个点的现象”转为“一个可复核的区间判断”，也更符合论文中对混沌识别的严谨写法。",
      "source_text_sha256": "b8c7539ca711929d2c1f8bd01c79e45df88c22204a3454eca102f2bf9de06fc3",
      "start_byte": 3896
    },
    {
      "end_byte": 4213,
      "focus_id": "F004",
      "source_text": "如果把它放到图上展示，还应在曲线旁标明扫描范围和加密区间，避免读者把单个采样点误读成普适阈值。",
      "source_text_sha256": "b50cc25e86e494376000cddef2b1c8d5af3c3c861205168632a5a4ac525fe2cb",
      "start_byte": 4072
    }
  ],
